room_title: Escape room "The Art Gallery" by Challenge Escape Rooms in New York
room_description: A unique piece of art you've had your eyes on for years is up for auction today. But you're not the only one who came here with the mindset to win, and your rival has decided to play dirty. He has locked you in a secluded part of the gallery! The auction starts in an hour, will you be able to make it out on time?
